name: The Soul Of Nature
description:
THE SOUL OF NATURE
I have been waiting for the chaotic world, so i can rise up to take over the world. Human become mad and ignore the environment. I let it happen beacuse this not my time. Human never realize that nature has the power of a soul that will rise in the future. 
The reason human madness is demon, now I'll fight for life and make a better world.
